snippet.title: Gran Turismo Concept: 2001 Tokyo (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Gran Turismo Concept: 2001 Tokyo (PS2) - Car: Honda Integra Type R - Course: Mid-Field Raceway

The 2001 Tokyo version features Tokyo Motor Show 2001 concept cars including the Nissan GT-R Concept '01. 
Gran Turismo Concept is also the first in a series of future stand-alone expansion packs that has new cars and new tracks to Gran Turismo 3: A-Spec.
